1
00:00:08,600 --> 00:00:10,961
♪Love's little quiz
takes seven parts sweet♪

2
00:00:10,962 --> 00:00:13,559
♪And three parts bitter,
till you and I meet♪

3
00:00:13,560 --> 00:00:17,159
♪I pretend I'm not there,
but secretly stay♪

4
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:26,399
♪Waiting for you♪

5
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:31,400
♪We've got so many
romantic dreams to unfold♪

6
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:36,224
♪Finally hearing
the I love you I long to hold♪

7
00:00:36,225 --> 00:00:39,839
♪Falling fast
into the swirl of your eyes♪

8
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:42,399
♪It's just too tempting, so tempting♪

9
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:45,499
♪Never could I have guessed♪

10
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:46,499
♪My heart's rhythm♪

11
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:49,632
♪How beautiful it is, meeting you♪

12
00:01:02,975 --> 00:01:05,961
=Late to Love=
(Adapted from "My Husband Is A Billionaire!")

13
00:01:05,962 --> 00:01:08,640
=Episode 2=

14
00:01:15,419 --> 00:01:17,778
(Could my contract wife)

15
00:01:17,779 --> 00:01:20,340
(be my cousin's first love?)

16
00:01:20,637 --> 00:01:22,099
(Four Years Ago, Linhai Medical University)

17
00:01:22,100 --> 00:01:23,620
Stop following me.

18
00:01:24,540 --> 00:01:25,698
Xu Nange,

19
00:01:25,699 --> 00:01:27,579
that pipette won't stop me.

20
00:01:28,820 --> 00:01:30,780
Please stop following me.

21
00:01:30,979 --> 00:01:32,218
Not until you say yes.

22
00:01:32,219 --> 00:01:33,338
I'm not giving up.

23
00:01:33,339 --> 00:01:35,459
I'm not into dating.

24
00:01:35,460 --> 00:01:36,379
Got it?

25
00:01:37,419 --> 00:01:38,299
Xu Nange.

26
00:01:39,219 --> 00:01:40,739
So it's dating you hate, not me.

27
00:01:40,740 --> 00:01:41,900
Trust me.

28
00:01:42,020 --> 00:01:43,819
I'll give you an amazing life.

29
00:01:45,419 --> 00:01:46,338
I think

30
00:01:46,339 --> 00:01:47,459
you should work

31
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:48,860
on your own life first.

32
00:01:50,540 --> 00:01:52,338
Your family must be rich.

33
00:01:52,339 --> 00:01:53,338
But all I see

34
00:01:53,339 --> 00:01:55,739
is a spoiled rich kid wasting his life.

35
00:01:56,940 --> 00:01:58,019
Sorry.

36
00:02:19,819 --> 00:02:21,658
I was pretty awful back then.

37
00:02:21,659 --> 00:02:23,459
When I come back this time,

38
00:02:23,460 --> 00:02:25,419
I hope you'll accept me.

39
00:02:32,499 --> 00:02:33,699
Mr. Huo.

40
00:02:41,700 --> 00:02:42,819
Mr. Huo.

41
00:02:44,499 --> 00:02:46,300
What's wrong, Mr. Huo?

42
00:02:53,020 --> 00:02:55,379
How much did Xu Nange pay you?

43
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:58,299
Huh?

44
00:02:58,300 --> 00:03:00,938
I don't know what you mean.

45
00:03:00,939 --> 00:03:02,098
She's the senior

46
00:03:02,099 --> 00:03:03,739
Zichen loved for years.

47
00:03:03,740 --> 00:03:05,259
Don't tell me you didn't know.

48
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:06,060
I...

49
00:03:06,420 --> 00:03:08,539
I really didn't, Mr. Huo.

50
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:12,740
Then you botched the background check.

51
00:03:12,819 --> 00:03:13,459
I...

52
00:03:13,460 --> 00:03:15,060
Xu Nange

53
00:03:15,180 --> 00:03:16,778
broke Zichen's heart,

54
00:03:16,779 --> 00:03:18,979
then signed the marriage contract.

55
00:03:19,420 --> 00:03:21,259
Are you two in this together?

56
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:25,939
I'm innocent!

57
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:27,060
Mr. Huo...

58
00:03:28,619 --> 00:03:29,740
Here's what happened.

59
00:03:29,779 --> 00:03:31,498
I only did what you asked.

60
00:03:31,499 --> 00:03:32,778
Out of all the candidates,

61
00:03:32,779 --> 00:03:33,938
she seemed like a fit,

62
00:03:33,939 --> 00:03:35,058
so I gave you her file.

63
00:03:35,059 --> 00:03:35,579
Right?

64
00:03:35,580 --> 00:03:37,139
You made the final call.

65
00:03:37,140 --> 00:03:38,179
You chose her.

66
00:03:38,180 --> 00:03:38,899
You liked

67
00:03:38,900 --> 00:03:40,618
her research skills, medical background,

68
00:03:40,619 --> 00:03:41,378
and thought

69
00:03:41,379 --> 00:03:43,299
she might help
with Old Mrs. Huo's condition.

70
00:03:43,300 --> 00:03:43,899
So...

71
00:03:43,900 --> 00:03:44,900
Besides,

72
00:03:44,939 --> 00:03:46,459
if I had an agenda,

73
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:49,620
why would I bring more resumes
yesterday for you to review? Right?

74
00:03:54,219 --> 00:03:55,379
Mr. Huo,

75
00:03:55,499 --> 00:03:57,180
you tricked me?

76
00:03:57,700 --> 00:03:58,658
Then tell me.

77
00:03:58,659 --> 00:04:00,019
Why would she agree

78
00:04:00,020 --> 00:04:01,220
to a temporary marriage?

79
00:04:01,779 --> 00:04:02,938
Her file says

80
00:04:02,939 --> 00:04:04,778
family and school reasons.

81
00:04:04,779 --> 00:04:06,419
I'm not sure about the family part.

82
00:04:06,420 --> 00:04:07,498
As for school,

83
00:04:07,499 --> 00:04:09,139
she probably needs

84
00:04:09,140 --> 00:04:10,939
three more months for her thesis.

85
00:04:11,939 --> 00:04:13,618
The current rules say

86
00:04:13,619 --> 00:04:14,899
married PhD and master's students

87
00:04:14,900 --> 00:04:16,019
can take marriage leave.

88
00:04:16,020 --> 00:04:17,738
She must be

89
00:04:17,739 --> 00:04:18,859
out of options.

90
00:04:20,099 --> 00:04:20,778
Get the car.

91
00:04:20,779 --> 00:04:21,298
Find her.

92
00:04:21,299 --> 00:04:22,418
What will you do?

93
00:04:22,419 --> 00:04:23,738
I'll teach her

94
00:04:23,739 --> 00:04:25,340
where the line is.

95
00:04:33,859 --> 00:04:35,379
So you do answer calls.

96
00:04:35,380 --> 00:04:37,379
Busy as always, Dr. Big Shot?

97
00:04:37,380 --> 00:04:38,298
Say it,

98
00:04:38,299 --> 00:04:39,259
or I'm hanging up.

99
00:04:39,260 --> 00:04:39,899
Fine.

100
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:41,259
I'll make it quick.

101
00:04:41,260 --> 00:04:42,259
Just letting you know,

102
00:04:42,260 --> 00:04:44,259
your room is becoming
a walk-in closet.

103
00:04:44,260 --> 00:04:45,499
Come get

104
00:04:45,500 --> 00:04:46,338
all your junk,

105
00:04:46,339 --> 00:04:47,499
or I'm throwing it out.

106
00:04:47,500 --> 00:04:48,499
I'll come tomorrow.

107
00:04:48,500 --> 00:04:49,900
Don't touch anything.

108
00:04:50,299 --> 00:04:52,098
Who wants your trash?

109
00:04:52,099 --> 00:04:52,658
You know what?

110
00:04:52,659 --> 00:04:54,218
Just marry someone already

111
00:04:54,219 --> 00:04:56,019
and stop showing up here.

112
00:04:56,020 --> 00:04:57,218
You're annoying.

113
00:04:57,219 --> 00:04:58,019
Fine.

114
00:04:58,020 --> 00:04:59,979
Then wait for my good news.

115
00:05:14,419 --> 00:05:15,979
Why are you here?

116
00:05:16,299 --> 00:05:18,820
House calls weren't in the contract.

117
00:05:19,179 --> 00:05:20,380
You live here?

118
00:05:21,419 --> 00:05:22,299
Yeah.

119
00:05:22,779 --> 00:05:24,900
Don't come in if you're judging.

120
00:05:25,339 --> 00:05:26,538
I wasn't planning to.

121
00:05:26,539 --> 00:05:27,419
I...

122
00:05:29,099 --> 00:05:30,780
Not inviting me up?

123
00:05:42,820 --> 00:05:44,139
I came to ask you something.

124
00:05:44,140 --> 00:05:46,298
Why go through all this

125
00:05:46,299 --> 00:05:47,780
to get close to the Huo family?

126
00:05:48,020 --> 00:05:49,819
Get close to the Huo family?

127
00:05:49,820 --> 00:05:51,019
Huo Zichen.

128
00:05:51,020 --> 00:05:52,178
Explain that.

129
00:05:52,179 --> 00:05:53,738
Who's Huo Zichen?

130
00:05:53,739 --> 00:05:54,978
Your junior,

131
00:05:54,979 --> 00:05:56,580
and my cousin.

132
00:05:57,140 --> 00:05:59,780
I sort of remember him.

133
00:06:00,260 --> 00:06:01,220
Seriously?

134
00:06:01,419 --> 00:06:02,418
Are you Huo men

135
00:06:02,419 --> 00:06:04,298
all here to make my life harder?

136
00:06:04,299 --> 00:06:06,139
He chased me years ago,

137
00:06:06,140 --> 00:06:07,499
and I made it clear

138
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:09,260
that I didn't like him.

139
00:06:10,099 --> 00:06:11,178
So you rejected him

140
00:06:11,179 --> 00:06:12,340
to get to me?

141
00:06:13,419 --> 00:06:14,218
Huo Beiyan,

142
00:06:14,219 --> 00:06:15,858
are you that narcissistic?

143
00:06:15,859 --> 00:06:17,778
You asked me to marry you.

144
00:06:17,779 --> 00:06:18,459
Maybe you should

145
00:06:18,460 --> 00:06:20,260
get your head checked.

146
00:06:21,859 --> 00:06:22,940
Is that so?

147
00:06:23,580 --> 00:06:25,020
You were testing me?

148
00:06:26,380 --> 00:06:27,820
Just being careful.

149
00:06:28,820 --> 00:06:30,699
I can ignore many things,

150
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:32,940
but family is my line.

151
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:35,338
Zichen will be back in a week.

152
00:06:35,339 --> 00:06:36,538
So

153
00:06:36,539 --> 00:06:38,059
the deal is off.

154
00:06:38,219 --> 00:06:39,499
We're divorcing.

155
00:06:41,099 --> 00:06:42,780
Here's extra compensation.

156
00:06:43,625 --> 00:06:44,370
(Huo Trust Bank, 200,000 to Xu Nange)

157
00:06:48,460 --> 00:06:49,538
Works for me.

158
00:06:49,539 --> 00:06:50,619
I was worried

159
00:06:50,620 --> 00:06:51,699
this would get messy.

160
00:06:51,700 --> 00:06:52,699
Good deal.

161
00:06:52,700 --> 00:06:53,659
Let's divorce.

162
00:06:56,179 --> 00:06:56,939
Shen Yan,

163
00:06:56,940 --> 00:06:58,580
arrange the divorce tomorrow.

164
00:06:58,820 --> 00:06:59,699
What?

165
00:06:59,700 --> 00:07:00,979
Divorce?

166
00:07:01,099 --> 00:07:02,418
Mr. Huo, you're kidding, right?

167
00:07:02,419 --> 00:07:04,099
That's not possible.

168
00:07:04,260 --> 00:07:05,259
Why?

169
00:07:05,260 --> 00:07:07,460
There's a cooling-off period.

170
00:07:07,700 --> 00:07:08,499
How long?

171
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:09,658
One month.

172
00:07:09,659 --> 00:07:10,858
You won't be divorced

173
00:07:10,859 --> 00:07:12,220
before your cousin gets back.

174
00:07:17,779 --> 00:07:18,579
My money!

175
00:07:18,580 --> 00:07:19,939
Deal's off. The contract stays.

176
00:07:19,940 --> 00:07:20,418
You...

177
00:07:20,419 --> 00:07:22,179
Aren't you afraid he'll snap?

178
00:07:22,700 --> 00:07:24,700
There's a cooling-off period.

179
00:07:25,299 --> 00:07:26,780
Use your brain.

180
00:07:35,580 --> 00:07:36,459
Yin,

181
00:07:36,460 --> 00:07:37,899
listen to me.

182
00:07:37,900 --> 00:07:40,218
Getting an interview at Huo Group

183
00:07:40,219 --> 00:07:42,059
is only step one.

184
00:07:43,299 --> 00:07:45,139
What if he doesn't remember me?

185
00:07:45,140 --> 00:07:47,178
We only met once.

186
00:07:47,179 --> 00:07:49,098
Most women never even

187
00:07:49,099 --> 00:07:51,499
get that chance with Huo Beiyan.

188
00:07:51,580 --> 00:07:52,778
Besides,

189
00:07:52,779 --> 00:07:55,499
with that face of yours,

190
00:07:55,620 --> 00:07:57,619
you'll win him over.

191
00:07:58,060 --> 00:07:59,298
I'll make sure

192
00:07:59,299 --> 00:08:00,939
everything is perfect

193
00:08:00,940 --> 00:08:02,820
so you look your best.

194
00:08:03,659 --> 00:08:05,259
Is he really getting married?

195
00:08:05,260 --> 00:08:07,658
What if the source is wrong?

196
00:08:07,659 --> 00:08:09,098
Family first, career second.

197
00:08:09,099 --> 00:08:10,259
That's the Huo family rule.

198
00:08:10,260 --> 00:08:11,418
Everyone knows that.

199
00:08:11,419 --> 00:08:12,538
Huo Beiyan has officially

200
00:08:12,539 --> 00:08:13,778
taken over the family.

201
00:08:13,779 --> 00:08:15,260
Our Xu family

202
00:08:15,339 --> 00:08:16,900
has to seize this chance.

203
00:08:18,539 --> 00:08:19,419
Mom,

204
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:21,340
just wait for my good news.

205
00:08:23,500 --> 00:08:24,499
Xu Nange,

206
00:08:24,500 --> 00:08:25,699
keep it down.

207
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:26,979
You're so annoying.

208
00:08:28,539 --> 00:08:29,778
Is everything packed?

209
00:08:29,779 --> 00:08:30,899
Don't leave anything,

210
00:08:30,900 --> 00:08:32,979
or I'll throw it straight in the trash.

211
00:08:32,980 --> 00:08:33,899
Don't worry.

212
00:08:33,900 --> 00:08:35,979
I won't set foot here again.

213
00:08:36,459 --> 00:08:38,139
Came back for junk?

214
00:08:38,179 --> 00:08:39,820
How pathetic.

215
00:08:40,179 --> 00:08:40,979
Mom,

216
00:08:40,980 --> 00:08:42,499
I need a whole new look.

217
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:43,379
Of course.

218
00:08:43,380 --> 00:08:44,538
Use my card.

219
00:08:44,539 --> 00:08:45,698
You have to win

220
00:08:45,699 --> 00:08:46,899
Huo Beiyan's heart.

221
00:08:46,900 --> 00:08:47,739
(Huo Beiyan?)

222
00:08:47,740 --> 00:08:48,979
He's mine.

223
00:08:49,059 --> 00:08:50,220
Absolutely.

224
00:08:51,699 --> 00:08:53,739
What are you laughing at, Xu Nange?

225
00:08:55,939 --> 00:08:57,379
I'm not laughing.

226
00:08:57,380 --> 00:08:59,099
I'm not the smiling type.

227
00:09:00,380 --> 00:09:01,339
Then go cry

228
00:09:01,340 --> 00:09:02,899
in your crappy rental.

229
00:09:02,900 --> 00:09:04,219
I'm sick of seeing you.

230
00:09:04,220 --> 00:09:05,340
Xu Yin,

231
00:09:05,419 --> 00:09:06,938
haven't you heard?

232
00:09:06,939 --> 00:09:08,979
Huo Beiyan is already married.

233
00:09:09,140 --> 00:09:10,698
That's impossible.

234
00:09:10,699 --> 00:09:11,979
With the Huo family's status,

235
00:09:11,980 --> 00:09:12,938
if he got married,

236
00:09:12,939 --> 00:09:14,700
the whole city would know.

237
00:09:15,100 --> 00:09:16,099
Wait.

238
00:09:16,100 --> 00:09:17,180
What's that?

239
00:09:19,140 --> 00:09:20,499
A marriage certificate?

240
00:09:20,700 --> 00:09:22,499
(Marriage Certificate)
Xu Nange, you're married?

241
00:09:22,980 --> 00:09:24,339
You told me to get married,

242
00:09:24,340 --> 00:09:25,836
so I did.

243
00:09:25,837 --> 00:09:27,057
(Marriage Certificate)

244
00:09:27,620 --> 00:09:29,178
Let me see

245
00:09:29,179 --> 00:09:31,779
what broke loser you married.

246
00:09:33,059 --> 00:09:34,259
Why'd you snatch it?

247
00:09:34,260 --> 00:09:35,460
Embarrassed?

248
00:09:36,539 --> 00:09:37,979
Honestly?

249
00:09:37,980 --> 00:09:39,379
A little.

250
00:09:40,659 --> 00:09:41,058
I'm out.

251
00:09:41,059 --> 00:09:42,298
Good. Go.

252
00:09:42,299 --> 00:09:43,940
Don't ever come back.

253
00:09:55,579 --> 00:09:57,099
Same suitcase as mine?

254
00:09:57,939 --> 00:09:58,538
Wait.

255
00:09:58,539 --> 00:09:59,545
(Graduation Certificate)

256
00:09:59,579 --> 00:10:01,019
Isn't that mine?

257
00:10:01,020 --> 00:10:02,418
Please move, Mrs. Huo.

258
00:10:02,419 --> 00:10:03,219
Wait.

259
00:10:03,220 --> 00:10:04,899
Who told you to move this?

260
00:10:07,579 --> 00:10:09,139
I did.

261
00:10:16,459 --> 00:10:17,418
Huo Beiyan,

262
00:10:17,419 --> 00:10:18,458
you again?

263
00:10:18,459 --> 00:10:19,058
Turns out

264
00:10:19,059 --> 00:10:20,619
you're the real schemer.

265
00:10:20,620 --> 00:10:21,219
Can't deal

266
00:10:21,220 --> 00:10:22,099
with your cousin,

267
00:10:22,100 --> 00:10:23,820
so you take it out on my stuff?

268
00:10:24,699 --> 00:10:25,859
Very funny.

269
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:28,259
What do you want?

270
00:10:28,419 --> 00:10:29,660
Starting today,

271
00:10:29,819 --> 00:10:31,300
you're moving in with me.

272
00:10:31,579 --> 00:10:32,739
What?

273
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:34,619
Come on, Dad.

274
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:36,538
That's not even a family rule.

275
00:10:36,539 --> 00:10:38,899
I'm doing this for your grandma's peace of mind.

276
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:39,739
Besides,

277
00:10:39,740 --> 00:10:41,859
you're already legally married.

278
00:10:41,860 --> 00:10:44,460
Why can't she live with us?

279
00:10:44,980 --> 00:10:47,259
Her family is more traditional.

280
00:10:48,100 --> 00:10:49,460
We'll talk after the wedding.

281
00:10:50,260 --> 00:10:52,019
Then come to the board dinner in two days,

282
00:10:52,020 --> 00:10:54,298
dressed properly.

283
00:10:54,299 --> 00:10:56,060
That shouldn't be a problem, right?

284
00:10:57,340 --> 00:10:58,458
She's...

285
00:10:58,459 --> 00:10:59,778
pretty busy lately.

286
00:10:59,779 --> 00:11:00,979
She has no time.

287
00:11:01,819 --> 00:11:02,698
As the Huo family's

288
00:11:02,699 --> 00:11:04,139
daughter-in-law,

289
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:06,418
she should be there.

290
00:11:06,419 --> 00:11:07,859
Anyway, I... I'll listen to Grandma.

291
00:11:07,860 --> 00:11:09,178
Yes, listen to Grandma.

292
00:11:09,179 --> 00:11:12,499
Listen to her? You're taking advantage
of her not being able...

293
00:11:12,500 --> 00:11:14,220
- Come home. Good.
- I...

294
00:11:14,819 --> 00:11:16,339
Come home.

295
00:11:16,340 --> 00:11:18,700
Home will be livelier.

296
00:11:19,860 --> 00:11:21,658
That's my mom.

297
00:11:21,659 --> 00:11:22,778
When it matters,

298
00:11:22,779 --> 00:11:24,298
you never miss.

299
00:11:24,299 --> 00:11:25,580
Still got it.

300
00:11:25,620 --> 00:11:26,538
My grandson...

301
00:11:26,539 --> 00:11:27,619
No, you brat.

302
00:11:27,620 --> 00:11:30,540
You heard your grandma.

303
00:11:34,299 --> 00:11:35,739
I get that you want

304
00:11:35,740 --> 00:11:37,220
to be a good grandson.

305
00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:39,178
But why move my things?

306
00:11:39,179 --> 00:11:40,499
I'm not moving.

307
00:11:46,140 --> 00:11:47,298
Xu Nange,

308
00:11:47,299 --> 00:11:48,578
this isn't up for debate.

309
00:11:48,579 --> 00:11:50,859
Huo Beiyan, I'm not asking
for your permission either.

310
00:11:50,860 --> 00:11:52,660
All we signed was...

311
00:11:54,579 --> 00:11:56,060
Keep it down.

312
00:11:56,380 --> 00:11:57,660
I know.

313
00:11:58,340 --> 00:12:00,859
All we signed
was a fake marriage contract,

314
00:12:00,860 --> 00:12:02,058
not a slave contract.

315
00:12:02,059 --> 00:12:03,099
Where does it say

316
00:12:03,100 --> 00:12:04,739
I have to move in with you?

317
00:12:04,779 --> 00:12:06,178
That's unreasonable.

318
00:12:06,179 --> 00:12:08,660
And honestly, not safe for me.

319
00:12:10,179 --> 00:12:11,580
Not safe?

320
00:12:12,020 --> 00:12:13,418
What are you scared of?

321
00:12:13,419 --> 00:12:14,700
That I'll eat you?

322
00:12:15,380 --> 00:12:16,460
Huo Beiyan,

323
00:12:16,779 --> 00:12:17,739
do you really think

324
00:12:17,740 --> 00:12:19,899
every woman wants you?

325
00:12:19,900 --> 00:12:21,540
Why should I go along with this?

326
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:25,499
Because you signed it.

327
00:12:26,419 --> 00:12:27,938
If divorce didn't take a month,

328
00:12:27,939 --> 00:12:29,499
I'd already be gone.

329
00:12:31,140 --> 00:12:33,058
Besides, Zichen finding out doesn't scare me.

330
00:12:33,059 --> 00:12:34,540
It scares you.

331
00:12:40,100 --> 00:12:41,458
Then what exactly

332
00:12:41,459 --> 00:12:43,499
will make you cooperate?

333
00:12:45,340 --> 00:12:47,979
Now that's a better attitude.

334
00:12:48,220 --> 00:12:48,899
Let's be honest.

335
00:12:48,900 --> 00:12:50,219
You need my help

336
00:12:50,220 --> 00:12:51,298
to reassure your grandma

337
00:12:51,299 --> 00:12:52,538
and answer to the Huo family.

338
00:12:52,539 --> 00:12:53,099
Fine.

339
00:12:53,100 --> 00:12:54,538
I get all that.

340
00:12:54,539 --> 00:12:55,619
But I, Xu Nange,

341
00:12:55,620 --> 00:12:57,259
respond to kindness, not threats.

342
00:12:58,699 --> 00:13:01,899
I want you to show some real sincerity
and beg me nicely,

343
00:13:02,380 --> 00:13:04,139
instead of using that arrogant CEO tone

344
00:13:04,140 --> 00:13:05,458
to micromanage my life.

345
00:13:05,459 --> 00:13:06,658
You think you look cool?

346
00:13:06,659 --> 00:13:08,058
You want me to beg you?

347
00:13:08,059 --> 00:13:08,899
I...

348
00:13:30,825 --> 00:13:34,599
♪What destiny brought us to meet♪

349
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:37,920
♪Two different worlds, a love so sweet♪

350
00:13:37,925 --> 00:13:41,299
♪A wish we made
in a past life, it seems♪

351
00:13:41,300 --> 00:13:44,154
♪Destined to cross time and dream ♪

352
00:13:44,155 --> 00:13:47,995
♪Like a fairytale story told♪

353
00:13:48,075 --> 00:13:51,332
♪A gentle breeze feels so bold♪

354
00:13:51,350 --> 00:13:55,036
♪As your hair brushes past your ear♪

355
00:13:55,037 --> 00:13:57,394
♪I long to kiss your cheek, my dear♪

356
00:13:57,395 --> 00:14:01,634
♪All my longing, all my love for you♪

357
00:14:01,635 --> 00:14:04,195
♪Has never changed, it's forever true♪

358
00:14:04,637 --> 00:14:11,035
♪It's the hand of fate
that we meet again♪

359
00:14:11,837 --> 00:14:16,275
♪Let me hold you once again♪

360
00:14:16,525 --> 00:14:19,445
♪Resting against your chest♪

361
00:14:19,795 --> 00:14:25,036
♪Your warmth shines like stars at night♪

362
00:14:25,037 --> 00:14:29,836
♪Let me kiss you once again♪

363
00:14:29,837 --> 00:14:32,636
♪No reason needed♪

364
00:14:32,637 --> 00:14:34,834
♪My heart belongs to you♪

365
00:14:34,835 --> 00:14:40,555
♪I'm not afraid
to cross time to find you♪

